Pricing
=======

Simple Pricing, No Hidden Fees.
-------------------------------

Creating an account is **completely free**, with no contract or credit-card required.  
You get **30 days** to try out our service before picking one of the options below.

Every account comes with a free gym website you can use right away.

*   ![Image 7: Small Plan Icon](https://gymdesk.com/images/site/pricing/small-plan.png)
    
    Micro Gym
    ---------
    
    Newly opened gyms up to 50 members.
    
    *   Up to 50 active members\*
    *   Unlimited staff accounts
    *   Responsive gym website
    *   All features included
    
    _$75_ / month
*   ![Image 8: Small Plan Icon](https://gymdesk.com/images/site/pricing/medium-plan.png)
    
    Small Gym
    ---------
    
    Smaller gyms up to 100 members.
    
    *   51-100 active members\*
    *   Unlimited staff accounts
    *   Responsive gym website
    *   All features included
    
    _$100_ / month
*   ![Image 9: Medium Plan Icon](https://gymdesk.com/images/site/pricing/large-plan.png)
    
    Medium Gym
    ----------
    
    Medium sized gym, up to 200 members.
    
    *   101-200 active members\*
    *   Unlimited staff accounts
    *   Responsive gym website
    *   All features included
    
    _$150_ / month
*   ![Image 10: Large Plan Icon](https://gymdesk.com/images/site/pricing/small-franchise.png)
    
    Large Gym
    ---------
    
    A larger gym, up to 400 members
    
    *   201-400 active members\*
    *   Unlimited staff accounts
    *   Responsive gym website
    *   All features included
    
    _$200_ / month
*   ![Image 11: Custom Plan Icon](https://gymdesk.com/images/site/pricing/custom.png)
    
    Enterprise
    ----------
    
    Get in touch for a custom plan for your needs.
    
    *   Custom
    *   Unlimited staff accounts
    *   Responsive gym website
    *   All features included
    
    [Contact Us](https://gymdesk.com/contact)

\* Visitors, frozen / cancelled members or prospects are not counted towards the active member count

You may cancel your account at any time, for no cost. All of your information can be exported out at your convenience.
